title: Why Not? vs Why Now?
itunes:title: Why Not? vs Why Now?
description:
Episode 178 - Are you a perfectionist? Most people think that they are. Perfectionism is just BS, it is a front for a real fear that you are hiding. In this episode I talk about perfectionism and how the quality of your life will be dictated by the quality of the questions you ask yourself, the small difference between why not and why now?
